title: 10/07: Injury Updates, Players to Trust and Buy or Sell (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Dr. David Chao stops by with the latest on Patrick Mahomes, Saquon Barkley, Mason Rudolph and more. And then we bring on Will Brinson and another great guest Mike Tagliere of FantasyPros! Should we  be concerned about the KC offense? What's the deal with their RBs? Is Melvin Gordon a Top 12 RB rest of season? Also can we trust James Conner, Larry Fitzgerald and a few others? We also have Buy or Sell and your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
